Originally:

Schematics of an interface board for connecting an iPad retina display (LP097QX1-SPA1) to a DisplayPort source.

Revised:

PCB for connecting an iPad 3 LCD screen to displayport and using an inexpensive capacitive touch screen digitizer as a USB multi-touch device.

Goals:
- Inexpensive (~$100)
- Accessible for modification
- Open source
- Simple construction 
  - PCB through OSH Park
  - Case through laser-cut acrylic
  - Parts throuh suppliers like AliExpress, Mouser
